The paper discusses optimization algorithms for nonconvex regularizers in sparse learning, compressed sensing, low-rank matrix learning, and total variation models. These topics are commonly studied in machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), information theory (cs.IT), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and signal processing (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
